<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Login - Politician Promise Tracker</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      background: #eee;
      padding: 50px;
    }
    .login-container {
      background: white;
      padding: 20px;
      border: 1px solid #ccc;
      max-width: 400px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }
    h1 {
      margin-bottom: 5px;
    }
    .subtitle {
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      font-size: 14px;
      color: #666;
    }
    .form-group {
      margin-bottom: 15px;
    }
    label {
      display: block;
      margin-bottom: 5px;
    }
    input {
      width: 100%;
      padding: 8px;
      border: 1px solid #999;
    }
    button {
      padding: 10px 20px;
      background: #0066cc;
      color: white;
      border: none;
      cursor: pointer;
    }
    .error {
      background: #ffcccc;
      padding: 10px;
      margin-bottom: 15px;
      border: 1px solid #cc0000;
    }
    .demo-info {
      margin-top: 20px;
      padding: 10px;
      background: #ffffcc;
      border: 1px solid #cccc00;
      font-size: 12px;
    }
    .demo-info h3 {
      margin: 0 0 10px 0;
    }
    .demo-info p {
      margin: 5px 0;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="login-container">
    <h1>Politician Promise Tracker</h1>
    
    <% if (error) { %>
      <div class="error"><%= error %></div>
    <% } %>
    
    <form method="POST" action="/login">
      <div class="form-group">
        <label for="username">Username:</label>
        <input type="text" id="username" name="username" required>
      </div>
      
      <div class="form-group">
        <label for="password">Password:</label>
        <input type="password" id="password" name="password" required>
      </div>
      
      <button type="submit">Login</button>
    </form>

    <div class="demo-info">
      <h3>Demo Accounts:</h3>
      <p>Admin: <strong>admin</strong> / <strong>admin123</strong></p>
      <p>Politicians:</p>
      <p>- <strong>monkolkiat</strong> / <strong>pass123</strong> (มงคลเกียรติ เจริญทรัพย์)</p>
      <p>- <strong>somying</strong> / <strong>pass123</strong> (สมหญิง รักชาติ)</p>
      <p>- <strong>somchai</strong> / <strong>pass123</strong> (สมชาย เสียเกียรติ)</p>
      <p>- <strong>phiangdin</strong> / <strong>pass123</strong> (เพียงดิน สุจริต)</p>
      <p>- <strong>anucha</strong> / <strong>pass123</strong> (อนุชา ดำรงค์)</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
